itemname: Designs for Health Probiotic Synergy Spheres - Patented Controlled Release Probiotic Spheres - Supplement for Adults with Bifidobacterium Longum + L Acidophilus (60 Spheres)
itemdescription: With probiotic supplements, it's all about the survival of three major barriers: during the manufacturing process, on the shelf and through stomach acid. Probiotic Synergy is formulated to survive these barriers with cutting edge technology that uses the most advanced patented delivery and shelf stability technology available to ensure maximum potency and viability. It is this Probiospheres tableting technology and shape that protects fragile probiotic organisms from harsh stomach acid and delivers the highest number of live organisms to the intestinal tract. The end result is higher potency, superior delivery, and minimal waste. Made with non-GMO ingredients.

itemname: Designs for Health Probiophage DF - Bacteriophage Prebiotic + Probiotic Supplement - Probiotics for Digestion + Immune Support - Dairy Free Pre and Pro Biotics in Delayed Release Capsules (60 Count)
itemdescription: Probiophage DF is a specialized bacteriophage formulation combining four types of phages (as the proprietary bacteriophage blend PrePhage) along with seven strains of probiotics. This product is designed to support the proliferation of beneficial bacteria throughout the small and large intestines in order to promote healthy GI and immune function. itemname: Designs for Health Liposomal Glutathione - Liquid Glutathione Supplement, 100mg with Enhanced Absorption - Detox + Immune System Support - Lemon Peppermint Flavored Drops (50 Servings / 1.7oz)
itemdescription: Liposomal Glutathione is an exciting glutathione product formulated with liposomal technology. Liposomes are spheres made of phospholipids, the primary building blocks of cell membranes. Owing to this structure, liposomes bond easily with cell membranes to facilitate intracellular delivery of their nutrient cargo. Thanks to this enhanced delivery and absorption, nutrients delivered in liposomal form offer superior absorption and bioavailability. Glutathione is one of the most powerful antioxidants naturally produced in the body, as it protects virtually every tissue.*

The most comprehensive formulation in Klaire Labs® Baseline Balance probiotic line, Vital-10® is a hypoallergenic, proprietary blend of 10 probiotic species developed specifically for the maintenance of a healthy intestinal microbiota.* Vital-10® provides a synergistic blend of indigenous, essential colonizing, and beneficial transient probiotics. itemname: Quicksilver Scientific Liposomal NAD+ Platinum - Liquid NAD-Precursor Supplement with Liposomal NMN, TMG + B12 - Healthy Aging, Cognitive, Liver + Energy Support - (3.38oz / 100ml)
itemdescription:
NAD+ Platinum is a blend of NMN, methylation cofactors and sirtuin activators. It combines the action of 3 separate products (NAD Gold, Methyl Charge and The One) to offer the most synergistic and complete longevity formula available.

NAD+ Platinum contains nicotinamide mononucleotide (NMN), a stable precursor of the longevity molecule NAD+. NAD+ is found in every cell in the body, which is essential for regulating cellular energy production, and mitochondrial function. Quercetin also has the benefit of acting as a senolytic, selectively neutralizing aging cells. TMG, riboflavin and vitamin B12 help maintain a healthy methylation cycle, a crucial element of cellular NAD+ production.

itemdescription: Change the way you age with NAD+ Gold, a next-generation age management elixir and the only liposomal source of NMN, the most direct and stable precursor to our body's natural 'anti-aging' molecule, NAD+. With the addition of TMG to support methylation, this powerful formula promotes the replenishment and rejuvenation of your cells and metabolism.

itemname: Quicksilver Scientific Membrane Mend - Brain, Cellular & Healthy Aging Support with Phosphatidyl Choline (PC), Vitamin E Tocotrienols, Ahiflower Oil & Astaxanthin Supplements (3.38oz / 100ml)
itemdescription:
High-grade PC (phosphatidyl choline), vitamin e tocotrienol and Ahiflower oil fatty acid complex, sync to help support membrane health. We need this smart barrier to maintain a healthy, energy-producing environment and keep out unwanted molecules, ions, and oxidative threats.* Unlike many lecithin supplements, Membrane Mend PC is derived from sun flower lecithin, tested soy protein free.

Phosphatidylcholine is the cornerstone of membrane lipid therapy and has been shown to support optimal energy production by fortifying mitochondrial composition. PC also supports healthy bile flow, and healthy liver and brain function.*

Astaxanthin is a pink-colored carotenoid found in marine life like krill, shrimp, and salmon. This carotenoid provides potent antioxidant benefits that support membrane integrity.*

Ahiflower is an essential fatty acid derived from Buglossoides arvensis seeds that contain an oil that provides an optimal ratio of omega-6 to omega-3 fatty acids shown to support the health and function of cell membranes.*

DeltaGold Tocotrienols vitamin E are compounds within the vitamin E family with powerful antioxidant properties. Delta tocotrienol in tocotrienols supplements is a highly bioavailable form that supports membrane integrity by offering protection from oxidative damage.*

Uses patent-pending Quicksilver Scientific Delivery Systems technology to create small, stable delivery vesicles (between 20-70 nm) that begin absorbing as soon as they hit the mouth.*

itemname: Anima Mundi PAU D'Arco - Pure Rainforest Superfood Herbal Powder from Peru - Add to Tea, Soup or Broth (4oz / 113g)
itemdescription:
Pau D'Arco - IPE ROXO - Tahuari aka Tree of Life

This product contains 100% Pau D'Arco bark organically grown and/or sustainably wildcrafted in Peru. Just put 1-2 tsp in your juice, smoothie or tea. As a tea, steep 0.5-1 Tbsp, in a cup of boiling water for 15 minutes and enjoy.

Preserving the Wisdom of Ancient Botany

These apothecary formulas are composed of the most pristine botanicals found in nature. Anima Mundi works directly with small farmers and supports true fair trade practices, permacultural outreach, and plant-based remedies that benefit people from all walks of life. All products are organic or wildcrafted, vegan, gluten free, non-GMO, and handcrafted in Brooklyn.
